targets.query: SELECT sum("value")  / 60 FROM "qtype" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT count("value") FROM "client_subnet2" WHERE "server" =~ /^$server$/ AND "node" =~ /^$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "clientsubnet" fill(0)
SELECT top("value", "tld", 10) FROM "qtype_vs_tld" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "tld" fill(0)
